name: Very Long
bio: This biography is intentionally very long to test the system's handling of large text fields. It contains multiple paragraphs of content. The author was born in a small town and grew up with a passion for writing. They published their first book at age 25 and went on to win numerous awards. Their work has been translated into over 50 languages and sold millions of copies worldwide. Critics have praised their unique writing style and compelling storytelling. They continue to write and inspire new generations of authors. This entry tests how the ETL system processes, transforms, and stores large amounts of textual data without truncation or corruption.
